{"tid":2339011,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"電動卡車大單告吹 Nikola 股價摔 10% 創上市來新低","createTime":"2020-12-24T10:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T11:44:45.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"492b66e420c02766ea42aa190b78a4164c720064","tid":2339011,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:45:40.000Z","msg":"先前電動卡車製造商 Nikola 股價表現亮眼，被視為電動車龍頭特斯拉（Tesla）的頭號挑戰者。但最新消息傳出，北美第二大固體廢棄物處理公司 Republic Services 決定取消訂單，2,500 輛電動垃圾車大單告吹，23 日 Nikola 股價崩跌高達逾 10%<br />\n<br />\nNikola 23 日股價重挫 10.70%、收 15.03 美元，創 6 月 4 日在那斯達克交易所公開上市以來新低。<br />\n<br />\nCNBC、《Barron&rsquo;s》等外媒報導，23 日，Nikola 和 Republic Services 終止合作關係，停止共同開發電動垃圾車，原因是開發時間比預期更長，並帶來過高的成本壓力，致使雙方做出這項決定。<br />\n<br />\nNikola 執行長 Mark Russell 發表聲明稱：「鑒於資源和投資所限，這對兩家公司都是正確的決定。」「我們支持並尊重 Republic Services 為客戶實現注重環保、永續解決方案的承諾。」<br />\n<br />\n今年 8 月 10 日，Nikola 與 Republic Services 達成供貨協議，Nikola 將出貨至少 2,500 輛電動垃圾車，最多上看 5,000 輛。據 Republic Services 表示，其續航力可達 150 英里，預計於 2023 年開始整合到現有車隊中。<br />\n<br />\n當天 Nikola 股價聞訊大漲，飆升 22.03% 至每股 44.81 美元，但目前股價僅剩當時的三分之一。<br />\n<br />\n今年 6 月，Nikola 以特殊目的併購公司（SPAC）為名義借殼上市，股價一度被炒作至近 100 美元，使市值略高於福特汽車（Ford Motor）。<br />\n<br />\n然而，Nikola 後來爆發連串醜聞，包括 9 月遭做空機構 Hindenburg Research 爆料誇大技術，電動卡車實際上路的影片，事實上只是從斜坡高處往下滑，引發 Nikola 創辦人 Trevor Milton 在數天後閃辭，股價也開始一落千丈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先前死都唔信Nikola係騙局的連仔們還好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313cc465c81490a75a27a1ffdb1cc536cb4507a6","tid":2339011,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://finance.technews.tw/2020/12/24/nikola-stock-price/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.technews.tw%2F2020%2F12%2F24%2Fnikola-stock-price%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=10fb5739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.technews.tw/2020/12/24/nikola-stock-price/</a>"},{"pid":"8139f2a2f53bdf499bc1d13b25d810d24a92c604","tid":2339011,"uid":131522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:47:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯Nokia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輸太多眼都喊到殘"},{"pid":"9e89af8c3058f1669bdd70170b8a451ca991c1a8","tid":2339011,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8139f2a2f53bdf499bc1d13b25d810d24a92c604","tid":2339011,"uid":131522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:47:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯Nokia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輸太多眼都喊到殘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3ed3501ee3a233df4eba5a82a62bb531b2a4f7","tid":2339011,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:49:44.000Z","msg":"叫TSLA收購佢就可以反彈 唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41c45eb122a48094840a76f3f4b73c9cbf90567","tid":2339011,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"係咪可以入TＳＬＡ喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無人挑戰到TＳＬＡ地位"},{"pid":"5c133fd685c1605a2669055f186ea3d1687d928e","tid":2339011,"uid":40267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"哩間空殼垃圾竟然呃到咁多傻鳩落沓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96450f330621655480c166de1181d3f39efe93c","tid":2339011,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5c133fd685c1605a2669055f186ea3d1687d928e","tid":2339011,"uid":40267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":